{"text_id":222933,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," free"," zero","-","range"," processes"," on"," networks",","," which"," are"," fundamental"," models"," in"," statistical"," physics"," describing"," the"," behavior"," of"," particles"," on"," a"," discrete"," structure","."," Our"," main"," objective"," is"," to"," understand"," the"," impact"," of"," network"," topology"," on"," the"," macroscopic"," properties"," of"," these"," processes",".","\n\n","To"," achieve"," this"," goal",","," we"," develop"," a"," novel"," theoretical"," framework"," that"," allows"," us"," to"," analyze"," the"," stationary"," distribution"," of"," the"," particle"," density"," on"," arbitrary"," networks","."," Our"," methodology"," combines"," techniques"," from"," linear"," algebra",","," probability"," theory",","," and"," graph"," theory"," to"," derive"," exact"," expressions"," for"," the"," stationary"," distribution","."," We"," also"," introduce"," a"," new"," family"," of"," graph"," invariants",","," which"," we"," call"," the"," zero","-","range"," cum","ulants",","," that"," fully"," characterize"," the"," stationary"," distribution"," and"," reveal"," essential"," information"," about"," the"," network"," topology",".","\n\n","Our"," approach"," enables"," us"," to"," solve"," various"," open"," problems"," in"," the"," literature",","," such"," as"," the"," equivalence"," of"," the"," current"," and"," diffusion"," constants"," on"," arbitrary"," networks"," and"," the"," precise"," phase"," diagram"," of"," zero","-","range"," processes"," on"," specific"," graph"," structures","."," Moreover",","," we"," provide"," a"," detailed"," analysis"," of"," the"," effect"," of"," network"," geometry"," on"," the"," particle"," density"," fluctuations",","," revealing"," the"," emergence"," of"," new"," universality"," classes"," in"," the"," scaling"," behavior",".","\n\n","The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," arises"," from"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," how"," microscopic"," interactions"," between"," particles"," give"," rise"," to"," macroscopic"," phenomena"," on"," complex"," networks","."," Our"," results"," contribute"," to"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," the"," fundamental"," principles"," governing"," the"," behavior"," of"," zero","-","range"," processes"," on"," networks"," and"," may"," have"," implications"," for"," other"," areas"," of"," science"," and"," engineering",","," such"," as"," traffic"," flow",","," epidemic"," spreading",","," and"," load"," balancing"," in"," computer"," networks","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}